48
00:04:12,280 --> 00:04:13,520
water,

49
00:04:13,780 --> 00:04:16,770
and energy.

50
00:04:20,070 --> 00:04:21,390
Enough energy?

51
00:04:24,600 --> 00:04:25,440
What does that mean?

52
00:04:27,530 --> 00:04:28,880
Why didn't you ask me

53
