how I responded to Fang Chi?

54
00:04:31,650 --> 00:04:33,200
You must've told him

55
00:04:34,360 --> 00:04:36,190
you could only be friends

56
00:04:36,760 --> 00:04:38,200
because you already got me.

57
00:04:38,560 --> 00:04:40,060
You're so confident, aren't you?

58
00:04:40,740 --> 00:04:41,580
That's not true.

59
00:04:42,180 --> 00:04:43,500
I'm not confident in myself

60
00:04:45,060 --> 00:04:46,100
but in you.

61
00:04:52,540 --> 00:04:54,140
Sweet talker.

62
00:04:56,460 --> 00:04:57,300
It seems

63
00:04:58,380 --> 00:04:59,460
you'll occupy

64
