my entire world.

65
00:05:19,900 --> 00:05:20,740
Shen Yi.

66
00:05:22,940 --> 00:05:24,100
I'll repay you with my world.

67
00:05:27,100 --> 00:05:27,940
Only you.

68
00:05:29,700 --> 00:05:30,580
No one else.

69
00:05:45,060 --> 00:05:45,900
Gu Yichen,

70
00:05:47,260 --> 00:05:48,380
I really love you.

71
