00:06:12,300 --> 00:06:13,580
(Operating)

78
00:06:28,860 --> 00:06:31,660
(Operating)

79
00:06:31,980 --> 00:06:33,540
(Even god is on my side.)

80
00:06:40,380 --> 00:06:41,420
I'm sorry.

81
00:06:43,420 --> 00:06:44,460
- Mr. Gu.
- Auntie Sun.

82
00:06:44,660 --> 00:06:45,700
How is Grandpa right now?

83
00:06:45,820 --> 00:06:47,300
Mr. Gu, you're finally here.

84
00:06:47,800 --> 00:06:49,080
It's all my fault!

85
00:06:49,220 --> 00:06:51,020
Chairman has a heart disease,

86
00:06:51,140 --> 00:06:52,230
but I wouldn't dare to

87
00:06:52,300 --> 00:06:53,420
tell you about his condition

88
00:06:53,500 --> 00:06:54,740
without his permission.

89
00:06:55,260 --> 00:06:56,300
It's all my fault!

90
00:06:56,900 --> 00:06:58,500
- How could this happen?
- It's my fault.

91
00:07:04,980 --> 00:07:05,820
Yichen.

92
00:07:07,140 --> 00:07:07,980
Don't worry too much.

93
00:07:08,740 --> 00:07:09,660
Grandpa is still in surgery.

94
00:07:10,660 --> 00:07:11,940
But I found the best doctor.

95
00:07:12,540 --> 00:07:13,640
He will be fine.

96
00:07:20,660 --> 00:07:22,180
The board has something urgent.

97
00:07:23,700 --> 00:07:24,540
I have to go.

98
00:07:55,060 --> 00:07:56,250
Thank you so much.

99
00:07:56,660 --> 00:07:57,500
I really appreciate it.

100
00:07:58,340 --> 00:07:59,460
Especially, Mr. Chen, thank you

101
00:07:59,740 --> 00:08:01,580
for blocking the information
about my grandpa.

102
00:08:02,340 --> 00:08:03,180
Otherwise,

103
00:08:03,300 --> 00:08:04,290
the situation

104
00:08:04,980 --> 00:08:06,460
of Dayuan Group might get worse.

105
00:08:07,220 --> 00:08:08,060
Mr. Shang,

106
00:08:08,260 --> 00:08:09,250
