107
00:08:09,540 --> 00:08:11,310
This is what we should do.

108
00:08:11,460 --> 00:08:12,780
If we didn't block the media

109
00:08:12,910 --> 00:08:14,160
but let them report recklessly,

110
00:08:14,460 --> 00:08:15,540
the stock price

111
00:08:15,820 --> 00:08:16,820
would drop,

112
00:08:17,260 --> 00:08:18,580
and we'd be in big trouble.

113
00:08:19,780 --> 00:08:20,620
Mr. Shang,

114
00:08:20,820 --> 00:08:22,100
don't be so polite with us.

115
00:08:22,540 --> 00:08:23,460
Your grandfather

116
00:08:23,660 --> 00:08:24,530
and we built

117
00:08:24,540 --> 00:08:25,540
Dayuan Auto together.

118
00:08:26,180 --> 00:08:27,660
How could we stand by?

119
00:08:32,740 --> 00:08:33,580
Okay.

120
00:08:35,020 --> 00:08:35,900
Then I will get to

121
00:08:36,340 --> 00:08:37,180
the point.

122
00:08:37,980 --> 00:08:38,820
My grandpa is ill,

123
00:08:39,220 --> 00:08:40,660
and we don't know when he'll wake up,

124
00:08:41,260 --> 00:08:43,460
but there must be a chairman.

125
00:08:44,180 --> 00:08:45,220
So we must activate

126
00:08:45,380 --> 00:08:46,540
the emergency regulations

127
00:08:47,060 --> 00:08:47,900
and hold a board meeting

128
00:08:48,420 --> 00:08:49,540
to elect a new chairman.

129
00:08:50,820 --> 00:08:51,980
At tomorrow's board meeting,

130
00:08:53,100 --> 00:08:55,020
I hope you can support me

131
00:08:55,900 --> 00:08:56,740
and vote for me.

132
00:08:57,900 --> 00:08:58,780
I definitely won't

133
00:08:58,780 --> 00:08:59,780
let you down.

134
00:09:01,780 --> 00:09:02,620
What do you think?

135
00:09:09,900 --> 00:09:10,900
We're all aware of

136
00:09:11,220 --> 00:09:12,180
your ability.

137
00:09:13,220 --> 00:09:14,380
Currently, Dayuan Group

138
00:09:14,540 --> 00:09:15,380
needs a leader

139
00:09:15,580 --> 00:09:17,500
with vision and courage.

140
00:09:17,980 --> 00:09:20,380
I support Mr. Shang
becoming the new chairman.

141
00:09:22,860 --> 00:09:23,700
Right now,

142
00:09:24,580 --> 00:09:25,420
the chairman

143
00:09:26,220 --> 00:09:27,060
is in hospital.

144
00:09:27,980 --> 00:09:29,260
With you managing everything,

145
00:09:29,620 --> 00:09:30,900
I don't think anything

146
00:09:31,180 --> 00:09:32,620
will go wrong for now.

147
00:09:33,750 --> 00:09:34,780
In my opinion,

148
00:09:35,220 --> 00:09:36,540
maybe we should

149
00:09:36,980 --> 00:09:38,980
postpone the election

150
00:09:39,300 --> 00:09:40,860
until the chairman recovers...

151
00:09:40,860 --> 00:09:42,300
To be honest, I know

152
00:09:42,300 --> 00:09:43,220
what you're thinking.

153
00:09:46,420 --> 00:09:47,300
You know

154
00:09:48,140 --> 00:09:50,100
