to take over the company.

155
00:09:50,780 --> 00:09:52,060
Therefore, you're afraid

156
00:09:52,220 --> 00:09:53,620
if I become the chairman,

157
00:09:54,100 --> 00:09:54,960
Grandpa will blame you

158
00:09:54,980 --> 00:09:55,980
when he wakes up.

159
00:09:56,540 --> 00:09:57,660
Have you thought about this?

160
00:09:58,060 --> 00:10:00,140
First, my brother Gu Yichen

161
00:10:01,020 --> 00:10:02,620
is focused on racing

162
00:10:03,220 --> 00:10:04,740
and only wants to be
a professional driver.

163
00:10:05,020 --> 00:10:06,460
He has never and can't

164
00:10:06,700 --> 00:10:08,220
manage the group.

165
00:10:08,500 --> 00:10:09,500
Moreover, now he's

166
00:10:09,500 --> 00:10:10,780
still working for our rival,

167
00:10:10,780 --> 00:10:12,340
Changgu Racing Team.

168
00:10:13,060 --> 00:10:14,300
Well, even if he returns,

169
00:10:14,660 --> 00:10:16,100
will he prioritize Dayuan Group's

170
00:10:16,100 --> 00:10:17,260
interests?

171
00:10:21,100 --> 00:10:22,060
Second,

172
00:10:23,220 --> 00:10:24,420
Grandpa's illness

173
00:10:25,180 --> 00:10:26,460
is really serious

174
00:10:26,820 --> 00:10:27,780
this time.

175
00:10:28,220 --> 00:10:29,300
I've consulted

176
00:10:29,580 --> 00:10:31,140
many renowned experts.

177
00:10:31,140 --> 00:10:32,100
However,

178
00:10:33,340 --> 00:10:36,020
