179
00:10:41,300 --> 00:10:43,140
This is a critical time

180
00:10:43,140 --> 00:10:44,540
for Dayuan Group's survival.

181
00:10:44,900 --> 00:10:46,540
I hope you can make the right choice

182
00:10:46,740 --> 00:10:48,060
