191
00:11:17,660 --> 00:11:22,100
(Dayuan Group)

192
00:11:32,780 --> 00:11:33,740
Gu Yichen.

193
00:11:35,460 --> 00:11:36,620
How's your grandpa?

194
00:11:38,420 --> 00:11:39,380
Grandpa...

195
00:11:40,100 --> 00:11:41,260
