198
00:11:58,900 --> 00:12:00,700
They'll hold a board meeting

199
00:12:01,180 --> 00:12:02,460
to elect a new chairman.

200
00:12:03,660 --> 00:12:04,620
Shen Yi.

201
00:12:05,580 --> 00:12:06,740
I have to go back for Grandpa.

202
00:12:10,020 --> 00:12:11,300
As for the press conference...

203
00:12:12,740 --> 00:12:13,700
Just go back.

204
00:12:14,260 --> 00:12:15,260
I can handle it.

205
00:12:21,820 --> 00:12:22,780
Thank you.

206
00:12:32,380 --> 00:12:33,340
